xjadeo is a very simple video player that gets sync from jack. 

please refer to the documentation in the doc/ for any details!

 Build Instructions for the impatient:

 ./autogen.sh
 ./configure
 make 
 make install

-------------------------------------------
BUILD DEPENDANCIES
-------------------------------------------

you need have the devel packages installed on the system to compile xjadeo:
 * ffmpeg-devel  -  ffmpeg (0.4.9-6)
 * jack-audio-connection-kit-devel
 * libX11 

optionally you may want to have
 * freetype2
 * gtk
 * imlib         - Imlib (1.9.13-19) or Imlib11-dev (1.9.14-28)
 * SDL
 * portmidi
 * alsamidi

